pageTitle: Itinerary for Tuesday, January 19, 2016 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Itinerary for the Prime Minister, Justin Trudeau, for Tuesday, January 19, 2016:

St. Andrews by-the-Sea

8:30 a.m. The Prime Minister will be in a private Cabinet meeting.

Fredericton

11:50 a.m. The Prime Minister will depart for Davos-Klosters, Switzerland, to attend the World Economic Forum.

Please note: all times are local.

PMO Media Relations: 613-957-5555
